fields.definition: A human being, whether man, woman or child.
fields.name: Person

fields.definition: An organized group of people with a particular purpose, such as a business or government department.
fields.name: Organisation

fields.definition: A collection of information used for describing the location of an entity and/or details describing how the entity can be contacted.
fields.name: Address

fields.definition: A person that is authorised to represent an entity.
fields.name: Authorised Contact

fields.definition: A person or organisation that is somehow associated to another entity.
fields.name: Associated Entity

fields.definition: An electronic mechanism that allow entities to be contacted.
fields.name: Electronic Contact
